# BFSI Boilerplate

Full spec: `skills/skills_boilerplate.md`. API: `skills/skills_api_standards.md`. Auth: `skills/skills_auth.md`.

## Rules

- Feature-first: `lib/features/<name>/{domain,data,presentation}/` — dependencies inward only
- Riverpod: `StateNotifierProvider` per feature; repo provider wires datasource Impl internally
- Navigation: `go_router` + `AppRoutes` in `lib/app/router/app_router.dart`
- UI: Material 3 via `AppTheme`; shared widgets in `lib/core/widgets/`
- Errors: `Either<Failure, T>` from repository up; usecases for business rules

## New feature

Entity → abstract repo → usecase(s) → datasource + model + repo Impl → notifier + screen → route + tests under `test/`.

## Packages (approved)

flutter_riverpod · dio · go_router · hive · flutter_secure_storage · local_auth · dartz · equatable

## Do NOT

Business logic in widgets · Dio outside ApiClient · tokens in Hive · expose datasource as its own provider · hardcode routes/URLs/keys
